<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - My IPL Team Editor</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p, label {
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .contact-form {
            padding: 15px;
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 5px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        textarea {
            height: 100px;
            resize: none;
        }

        .btn-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: blue;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 120px;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: darkblue;
        }

        button a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
        }

        .redirect-button {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            background-color: blue;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .redirect-button:hover {
            background-color: darkblue;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>üèè Contact Us - My IPL Team Editor</header>
    <button class="redirect-button" onclick="window.location.href='/'">Go Home</button>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or issues, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section contact-form">
            <h2>Contact Form</h2>
            <form>
                <label for="name">Your Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Enter your name">

                <label for="message">Your Message</label>
                <textarea id="message" placeholder="Type your message here..."></textarea>

                <div class="btn-container">
                    <button id="call"><a href="tel:+1234567890">üìû Call Us</a></button>
                    <button id="mail"><a href="mailto:support@iplteam.com">üìß Mail Us</a></button>
                    <button id="chat"><a href="https://wa.me/1234567890">üí¨ Chat with Us</a></button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
